{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_10_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 うーっすら笑っとったなぁ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "……？　{user}さん？　お母さん？\n何かあったん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…? {user}-san? Mother?\nDid something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yumam001.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもないで。……それより、仕事が始まったら\n母親と娘やない。プロ同士やからね。分かってる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing at all. …More than that‚ once work starts‚\nwe're not mother and daughter. We're professionals. Understand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.1666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、分かってます。ほな、{user}さん\n精一杯頑張ってくるから、目離さんといてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I understand. Well then‚ {user}-san‚\nI'll do my very best‚ so don't take your eyes off me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.7333333969,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8433.3333333,
          "startTime": 29.1666667302
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.7333333969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ、頑張ってきてくれ。しっかり見てるから\n……部屋の隅っこで、目立たないように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah‚ do your best. I'll be watching closely…\n…from a corner of the room‚ inconspicuously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.5333333969
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7999996821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（読み合わせは順調だな。この後三十分の休憩か……）\n（なんとしても久美子さんの誤解を解かないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The script reading is going smoothly. There's a thirty-minute break after this…）\n（I have to clear up Kumiko-san's misunderstanding somehow.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9666667302,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3077.5843937000004,
          "startTime": 43.0442511239
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.8666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、うちの演技どうでした？\n台本、いーっぱい読んで練習してきたんやで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ how was my acting?\nI practiced a looot‚ reading the script again and again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.133328565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、凄く良かった。舞台とはまた違う良さがあったし\nセリフも立ち居振る舞いもとても自然だった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ it was really good. It had a different appeal from stage acting‚\nand both your lines and behavior were very natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.0999975205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんまに？　ママ、今の聞いた！？\n{user}さんがうちの演技自然やったって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Mama‚ did you hear that!?\n{user}-san said my acting was natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.6999949774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yumam002.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、さっきの優、よく出来とったなぁ\n本番までもう少し練習したら、ええ感じになるはずや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm-hm‚ Yu‚ you did really well just now.\nWith a little more practice before the actual performance‚ it should feel good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ママに演技のこと認めてもらえるんは嬉しいわ\n{user}さんも、ちゃんと見てくれてるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm happy that Mama acknowledges my acting.\nAnd {user}-san is watching me properly too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0666545232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.4333186468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、うち、今めっちゃ幸せや。大好きなママと\n{user}さんに褒めてもらって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I'm really happy right now. Being praised by\nmy beloved Mama and {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7333211899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "将来、こうやって三人で……ううん、パパも入れて\n四人で幸せに過ごすんが日常になるんかなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if someday this will be our everyday life—\nno‚ with Papa too‚ the four of us happily together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7999878566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.23332119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ、優！？\n今日は、その、あまり、そういうのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yu!?\nPlease‚ um… don't say such things today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9666570664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yumam003.m4a",
      "text": "……今日は、なんですねぇ\nふぅん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…\"Today‚\" you say.\nHmm…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.9333242418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違います！　いや、違わないんですけど……\n……俺は何を言っているんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ that's not it! Well‚ it's not exactly wrong‚ but…\n…What am I saying!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.0999939602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "変な{user}さんやなぁ。せや、この後は\n予定ないはずやし、今日は寮まで一緒に帰りましょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're being weird‚ {user}-san. Right‚ after this\nwe shouldn't have plans‚ so let's go back to the dorm together today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7333267849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.3666707356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yumam004.m4a",
      "text": "……ほんなら終わった後夕食でもご一緒にどうですか？\nじっくり、話さなあかんみたいですし、ねぇ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Then how about joining us for dinner after this?\nWe need to have a proper talk‚ don't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "…………も、もちろん\n喜んでご一緒させていただきます……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……O-of course.\nI'd be delighted to join you…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2211881913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A Few Days Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6000005724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 148.7000087104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、最近随分疲れてへん？\nどないしたん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you seem quite tired lately?\nWhat's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.7333339057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、体調悪いんちゃう？\n前に風邪で倒れたって聞いたし、帰って休んだ方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be that you're not feeling well?\nI heard you collapsed with a cold before‚ so you should go home and rest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2000005724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、明らかに別のことが原因なんだが……\nまぁ、これが優の通常運転だから仕方ないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's clearly caused by something else…\nWell‚ this is Yu's normal operation‚ so it can't be helped…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.8000005724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、うちのお母さんのせいやろ？\n最近やけに過保護なんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it‚ it's because of my mother‚ right?\nShe's been unusually overprotective lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.4000005724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "うちのことは{user}さんが、ちゃんと\n守ってくれるから安心してほしいって言ったんやけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told her that {user}-san properly\nprotects me‚ so she should feel at ease.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0666611356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "この前も、{user}さんとのことを\nしーっかり話して、念を押しておいたんやで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just the other day‚ I also talked things through with her\nabout us and firmly reassured her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.9333440783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
